caption: Figure 3: Win rates of our approach compared to DPO-SDXL and SDXL on human evaluation.
description: The bar chart presents the results of a user preference study comparing three different models: RankDPO, DPO-SDXL, and SDXL.  For each model, it shows the percentage of times users preferred its generated images over the others in a pairwise comparison.  RankDPO outperforms both DPO-SDXL and the baseline SDXL model, achieving a win rate above 56% compared to the other models, which had win rates below 60%. The chart uses horizontal bars to represent the win rate of each model, visually highlighting the superior performance of RankDPO.
